## 3. 

### 

 `src/main/index.ts`

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class MainWindow {
        +createWindow()
        +loadChatPage()
        +injectScripts()
        +manageSession()
    }
    
    class BubbleWindow {
        +createBubbleWindow()
        +showMessage()
        +handleUserInteraction()
    }
    
    class TodoManager {
        +createTodoWindow()
        +CRUDOperations()
        +injectTodoIcon()
    }
    
    class ScreenshotManager {
        +initScreenshot()
        +registerHotkey()
        +captureScreen()
    }
    
    class AutoUpdaterManager {
        +checkForUpdates()
        +downloadUpdate()
        +showUpdateDialog()
    }
    
    MainWindow --> TodoManager
    MainWindow --> ScreenshotManager
    MainWindow --> AutoUpdaterManager
    MainWindow --> BubbleWindow
```
